metadata.name: Death of Music
metadata.description:
The artwork is the first piece of "Death of Concepts".

It represents the day music dies. The concept of music is left somewhere desolate.

People are just watching it diminish. It is hanging on a tree that is either dead or alive.

This remains unknown to most. And one truth emerges from all other facts. 

It is prerogative of brave and sophisticated ones to tell about its annihilation.

D.T.
